[
  {
    "startTime": 0.201,
    "endTime": 2.801,
    "text": "I know I say this every morning but they're not moving."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.001,
    "endTime": 5.0,
    "text": "If you think there's no big deal, say something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.799,
    "endTime": 7.699,
    "text": "Oh my god, you think they're dead too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.75,
    "endTime": 8.401,
    "text": "I'll go check."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.781,
    "endTime": 13.5,
    "text": "Don't be dead, don't be dead, don't be dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.799,
    "endTime": 14.78,
    "text": "Oh, you're alive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.499,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "And you're alive!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.799,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "Okay, okay. Okay, I'm up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.151,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "Your breath smells good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.3,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "Uh, oh, I'm in...I'm in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.401,
    "endTime": 24.8,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.881,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "You can't just leave, guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.251,
    "endTime": 27.8,
    "text": "You gotta tell me where you're going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.799,
    "endTime": 30.8,
    "text": "Is that food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.859,
    "endTime": 31.377000000000002,
    "text": "Can I have some?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.797,
    "endTime": 33.8,
    "text": "Oh, you're spitting out...but can I have some?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.9,
    "endTime": 34.477,
    "text": "No?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.997,
    "endTime": 36.5,
    "text": "Stay right here, I'll go check on everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.001,
    "endTime": 39.199999999999996,
    "text": "I know where they are now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.2,
    "endTime": 39.799,
    "text": "Everything's fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.987,
    "endTime": 40.6,
    "text": "Cornelius, come eat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.898,
    "endTime": 41.300000000000004,
    "text": "I'm so hungry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.349,
    "endTime": 42.8,
    "text": "Oh I can't wait, I can't wait, I can't wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.9,
    "endTime": 43.6,
    "text": "Look, I'm even doing a trick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.869,
    "endTime": 44.9,
    "text": "That's how hungry I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.701,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "Faster, faster, faster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.301,
    "endTime": 49.2,
    "text": "Wait, I can eat this, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.401,
    "endTime": 49.900000000000006,
    "text": "This is food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.901,
    "endTime": 51.7,
    "text": "Because I've been getting some mixed signals lately."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.997,
    "endTime": 52.37,
    "text": "Is this food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.499,
    "endTime": 52.917,
    "text": "Not for you, buddy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.401,
    "endTime": 53.75,
    "text": "Is this food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.999,
    "endTime": 54.583000000000006,
    "text": "That's a jacket."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.598,
    "endTime": 55.8,
    "text": "This gotta be food, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.801,
    "endTime": 57.171,
    "text": "Are you sure?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.971,
    "endTime": 58.949999999999996,
    "text": "So you're sure this is food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.698,
    "endTime": 61.1,
    "text": "Oh yeah, this is really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.698,
    "endTime": 62.5,
    "text": "That can't be good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.5,
    "endTime": 63.2,
    "text": "We gotta hide!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.2,
    "endTime": 64.297,
    "text": "We gotta get out of here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.297,
    "endTime": 64.7,
    "text": "Whoah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.997,
    "endTime": 65.4,
    "text": "I'm okay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.259,
    "endTime": 68.496,
    "text": "Why are there clothes on the floor?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.497,
    "endTime": 69.5,
    "text": "Why don't they smell like us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.761,
    "endTime": 70.39999999999999,
    "text": "I can fix that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.451,
    "endTime": 70.88,
    "text": "Are you gonna help?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.241,
    "endTime": 72.7,
    "text": "Oh, there you are. - Uh-oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.8,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "Don't panic, I'm fine. - Cornelius!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.201,
    "endTime": 75.6,
    "text": "Don't worry about me, it's fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.801,
    "endTime": 78.87,
    "text": "Please come back inside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.499,
    "endTime": 82.69999999999999,
    "text": "That's not where you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.701,
    "endTime": 84.8,
    "text": "Excuse me, that's where you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.799,
    "endTime": 86.5,
    "text": "You go there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.396,
    "endTime": 89.6,
    "text": "Okay, guys, great news, I've finished cleaning my room and-"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.649,
    "endTime": 90.3,
    "text": "I can do a little sushi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.599,
    "endTime": 91.4,
    "text": "Eh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.597,
    "endTime": 91.89999999999999,
    "text": "Uh-oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.299,
    "endTime": 94.301,
    "text": "I'm not in the mood for sushi. - What's happening?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.396,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "What about some Thai food? - This is a nightmare."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.12,
    "endTime": 96.80000000000001,
    "text": "Eh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.901,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "I've never seen them fight like this before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.269,
    "endTime": 99.9,
    "text": "Just salads."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.53,
    "endTime": 100.999,
    "text": "I can't take this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.201,
    "endTime": 101.8,
    "text": "But then what are we gonna eat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.601,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Oh my god, they're not talking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.699,
    "endTime": 106.3,
    "text": "It's probably over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.799,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Okay, we're all freaked out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 109.4,
    "text": "This is upsetting because I love both of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.599,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "But I'm gonna live with her because we all know I love her more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.901,
    "endTime": 116.39999999999999,
    "text": "Okay, obviously things worked out, this is embarrassing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.698,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "But we all said things we didn't mean back there, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.2,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Thanks for letting me sleep in bed tonight, guys...you won't even know I'm here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.701,
    "endTime": 124.89999999999999,
    "text": "Hey, did you guys hear that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.4,
    "endTime": 126.4,
    "text": "Are you awake?"
  }
]